column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, e.bpt FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN PhotObj AS p ON p.objid=s.bestobjid  JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class LIKE &&&  AND e.bpt LIKE &&&
